ingredientsDesc:
#6C19
Microparticle：1 Bottle Recombinant Toxoplasma gondii antigen coated microparticles in MES buffer with protein stabilizers.
Conjugate：1 Bottle Murine acridinium-labeled anti-human IgG in MES buffer with protein stabilizers.
Assay Diluent：1 Bottle Toxo IgG assay diluent containing TRIS buffer with protein stabilizers.

#6C19-10
3 Bottle (8.0 mL each) of ARCHITECT Toxo IgG Controls：
	                Target Anti-Toxo IgG  
                                   Concentration   Control Range
Control	         Color          (IU/mL)	    (IU/mL)
CONTROL -        Natural	N/A	≤0.5
CONTROL 1  +   Natural	6.0	3.0 – 9.0
CONTROL 2  +   Natural	120.0	60.0 -180.0
# 6C19-01\n6 Bottles (4.0 mL each) of ARCHITECT Toxo IgG Calibrators. The calibrators are at the following concentrations：CAL A, CAL B, CAL C, CAL D, CAL E, CAL F：0, 5, 25, 50, 100, 200 (IU/mL)
